			<font class="lt4"><i>Assessment of viral genotype of hiv-1 in samples genotyped to the patients treated in the reference center dr. bruno piancastelli filho, londrina, pr municipality, during the year 2013 and analysis of possible codons resistance to anti-retroviral</i></font>
